rows.label: qst104503_msg001
rows.name: Placeholder event

rows.label: qst104503_msg0001
rows.name:
Good work, mo~ Everyone
arrived safely, mo!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0002
rows.name:
Now, to do business with the
Superbian army right away...mo...

rows.label: qst104503_msg0003
rows.name:
Sniff-sniff... Sniff-sniff...
Oh no, this is bad, mo.

rows.label: qst104503_msg0004
rows.name:
I smell the same scent as
the goods we brought from
all over the place, mo.

rows.label: qst104503_msg0005
rows.name:
Did our products overlap with the
military's supplies, mo?! We can't
sell anything like this, mo!!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0006
rows.name: Hmm, hmm... We'll procure locally, mo!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0007
rows.name:
We'll stock up on things that
can only be found in Temperantia
and sell them, mo!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0008
rows.name:
Your kind words are much appreciated,
mo. I'm moved to tears, mo.

rows.label: qst104503_msg0009
rows.name:
Well then, please bring me
materials that can be found
in Temperantia, mo!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0010
rows.name:
As long as we gather enough to
open the shop, it'll be fine, mo!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0011
rows.name: I'll be waiting, mo~!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0101
rows.name:
Did you bring things
from Temperantia, mo?

rows.label: qst104503_msg0102
rows.name:
Still looking for more products,
mo! I'll be waiting, mo~!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0201
rows.name:
I'd like you to get the
Metal Brooches, a treasure
among these soldiers, mo.

rows.label: qst104503_msg0202
rows.name: 10 Metal Brooches, please, mo~

rows.label: qst104503_msg0301
rows.name:
Sniff-sniff... Sniff-sniff...
I smell a treasure that can
only be sold here, mo!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0302
rows.name:
Metal Brooches! To Kukn, they don't
look like treasure at all, mo...

rows.label: qst104503_msg0303
rows.name:
But if there's a demand from
the soldiers here, it's a
Nopon's job to supply!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0304
rows.name:
We now have a satisfactory lineup
for our first shop opening, mo!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0305
rows.name:
By the way, where did
you find this, mo?

rows.label: qst104503_msg0306
rows.name:
At the coast right over
there, mo? Understood, mo.

rows.label: qst104503_msg0307
rows.name:
Kukn will use the Nopon art of stealth
to secretly gather treasure without
being found by monsters, mo!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0308
rows.name:
Thank you for your help, mo!
Please accept this reward, mo!
